what classes we might have in this game:
- entire deck
  - can contain cards
- dealer/hand can be attribute
- suits are constant... 

-methods:
- deal, stay, shuffle
  - these methods would belong to the Deck card
- hit would belong to player and dealer classes
- cards in hand are hand
- deck is compilation of 52 cards
- card in hand could go inside player class

Outline:
-classes
-names of methods
-where the methods go
-what the methods do
- for example
  - king of hearts attributes include:
    - suit
    - points
    - rank(what actually shows up on card face)

